'''朗格'''（{{Lang-de|'''A. Lange & Söhne'''}}），是[[德國|德國]]名贵钟表品牌、朗格公司（Lange Uhren GmbH）的[[注册商标|注册商标]]，1845年由费迪南德·阿道夫·朗格（Ferdinand Adolph Lange）在德国的[[格拉斯许特|格拉斯许特]]（Glashütte）创立。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=https://blog.crownandcaliber.com/history-lange-sohne/|title=The History of A. Lange and Sohne|date=2018-04-12|language=en-US|website=Crown & Caliber Blog|access-date=2018-12-14|archive-date=2021-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124022948/https://blog.crownandcaliber.com/history-lange-sohne/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite web|url=https://www.hautehorlogerie.org/en/brands/history/h/a-lange-soehne/|title=History - Fondation de la Haute Horlogerie|website=www.hautehorlogerie.org|access-date=2018-12-14|archive-date=2020-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201205231424/https://www.hautehorlogerie.org/en/brands/history/h/a-lange-soehne/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Lange Uhren GmbH: Private Company Information - Bloomberg|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/research/stocks/private/snapshot.asp?privcapId=39800269|work=www.bloomberg.com|accessdate=2019-03-07|archive-date=2019-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190307173905/https://www.bloomberg.com/research/stocks/private/snapshot.asp?privcapId=39800269|dead-url=no}}</ref> [[第二次世界大战|第二次世界大战]]之后，朗格被[[前苏联|前苏联]]和[[东德|东德]]国有化，朗格品牌消失。<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":1" /> 1990年，费迪南德·阿道夫·朗格的曾孙沃尔特·朗格（Walter Lange）重新注册朗格商标，朗格品牌才得以重建。<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":1" />

朗格是世界上最著名的名贵钟表品牌之一，而朗格公司于2000年起成为瑞士[[历峰集团|历峰集团]]（Richemont Group）的子公司。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.hautehorlogerie.org/en/brands/brand/s/a-lange-soehne/|title=A. Lange & Söhne - Fondation de la Haute Horlogerie|website=www.hautehorlogerie.org|access-date=2018-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190929032922/https://www.hautehorlogerie.org/en/brands/brand/s/a-lange-soehne/|archive-date=2019-09-29|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.lifestyleasia.com/style/watches/lange-sohne-reaffirms-reputation-serious-watchmaking-two-insider-releases/|title=A. Lange & Söhne reaffirms its reputation for serious watchmaking with two insider releases|date=2018-06-01|language=en-US|website=Lifestyle Asia|access-date=2018-12-14|archive-date=2018-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181216031817/https://www.lifestyleasia.com/style/watches/lange-sohne-reaffirms-reputation-serious-watchmaking-two-insider-releases/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.hodinkee.com/articles/a-week-on-the-wrist-the-a-lange-shne-lange-1-timezone|title=A Week On The Wrist: The A. Lange & Söhne Lange 1 Time Zone Luminous|last=October 24|first=Benjamin Clymer|language=en|last2=2012|website=HODINKEE|access-date=2018-12-14|archive-date=2020-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204174618/https://www.hodinkee.com/articles/a-week-on-the-wrist-the-a-lange-shne-lange-1-timezone|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":2">{{Cite web|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/elizabethdoerr/2018/04/17/making-history-unique-a-lange-sohne-1815-homage-to-walter-lange-gets-set-to-hit-auction-block/|title=Making History: Unique A. Lange & Söhne 1815 Homage To Walter Lange Gets Set To Hit Auction Block|last=Doerr|first=Elizabeth|language=en|website=Forbes|access-date=2018-12-14|archive-date=2019-08-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190831011644/https://www.forbes.com/sites/elizabethdoerr/2018/04/17/making-history-unique-a-lange-sohne-1815-homage-to-walter-lange-gets-set-to-hit-auction-block/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":12">{{Cite web|url=https://www.hautehorlogerie.org/en/brands/history/h/a-lange-soehne/|title=History - Fondation de la Haute Horlogerie|website=www.hautehorlogerie.org|access-date=2018-12-14|archive-date=2020-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201205231424/https://www.hautehorlogerie.org/en/brands/history/h/a-lange-soehne/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 朗格表在外形和设计上独具德国格拉斯许特的风格，贴近经典英伦风格，而与瑞士表的风格迥然不同。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://watchesbysjx.com/2018/03/understanding-watch-design-at-a-lange-sohne-with-help-from-the-experts.html|title=Understanding Watch Design at A. Lange & Söhne, With Help From the Experts {{!}} SJX Watches|website=watchesbysjx.com|access-date=2018-12-19|archive-date=2020-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127004855/https://watchesbysjx.com/2018/03/understanding-watch-design-at-a-lange-sohne-with-help-from-the-experts.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.hodinkee.com/brands/a--lange---sohne|title=A. Lange & Söhne|language=en|website=HODINKEE|access-date=2018-12-19|archive-date=2021-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210220080459/https://www.hodinkee.com/brands/a--lange---sohne|dead-url=no}}</ref> 朗格的旗舰表款包括朗格1号（Lange 1）以及朗格1815。

==历史==

=== 早期历史 ===
[[File:Ferdinand_Adolph_Lange.jpg|链接=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Ferdinand_Adolph_Lange.jpg]]
费迪南德·阿道夫·朗格（Ferdinand Adolph Lange）于1845年在德国[[萨克森自由州|萨克森自由州]]（Saxony）的[[格拉斯许特|格拉斯许特]]（Glashütte）建立。<ref name=":13">{{Cite web|url=https://www.hautehorlogerie.org/en/brands/history/h/a-lange-soehne/|title=History - Fondation de la Haute Horlogerie|website=www.hautehorlogerie.org|access-date=2018-12-14|archive-date=2020-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201205231424/https://www.hautehorlogerie.org/en/brands/history/h/a-lange-soehne/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="nytimes">{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2015/11/27/fashion/at-home-with-a-lange-sohne.html|title=At Home With A. Lange & Söhne|accessdate=24 May 2016|date=27 November 2015|work=The New York Times|archive-date=2015-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151206023331/http://www.nytimes.com/2015/11/27/fashion/at-home-with-a-lange-sohne.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 1868年，费迪南德之子理查德·朗格（Richard Lange）加入公司，公司更名为''朗格 & 儿子''（''A. Lange & Söhne''）''，''通称'''朗格'''。在朗格和其子理查德和Emil 的努力下，朗格公司生产出了高质量的怀表，最高质量的表会被标上“1A”的标记。<ref name="dna">{{cite web|url=http://www.dnaindia.com/lifestyle/report-when-passion-and-precision-meet-in-watchmaking-2146193|title=When passion and precision meet in watchmaking|accessdate=24 May 2016|date=17 November 2015|work=dna|archive-date=2016-02-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160219062606/http://www.dnaindia.com/lifestyle/report-when-passion-and-precision-meet-in-watchmaking-2146193|dead-url=no}}</ref>

朗格家族的后代继承经营公司，在[[第二次世界大战|第二次世界大战]]中，朗格与其它德国制表厂一样为德军制造大尺寸军用腕表。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/home/moslive/article-1245056/Vintage-watches-real-pedigree.html|title=Vintage watches with real pedigree|accessdate=24 May 2016|work=Mail Online|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304101537/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/home/moslive/article-1245056/Vintage-watches-real-pedigree.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

二战后，德国战败，1948年苏联将朗格公司财产国有化，朗格品牌消失。<ref name=":02">{{Cite web|url=https://blog.crownandcaliber.com/history-lange-sohne/|title=The History of A. Lange and Sohne|date=2018-04-12|language=en-US|website=Crown & Caliber Blog|access-date=2018-12-14|archive-date=2021-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124022948/https://blog.crownandcaliber.com/history-lange-sohne/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":13" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.alange-soehne.com/en/spirit|title=Brand Page|language=en|website=A. Lange & Söhne|access-date=2018-12-14|archive-date=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118005557/https://www.alange-soehne.com/en/spirit|dead-url=no}}</ref> 费迪南德·阿道夫·朗格的曾孙、时任公司总裁的沃尔特·朗格（Walter Lange）被迫逃离德国。<ref name=":13" />

=== 近期发展 ===
[[東德|东德]]、[[西德|西德]]统一后，1990年12月，沃尔特·朗格在制表业高管Günter Blümlein 以及瑞士表业同行（包括[[积家|积家]]和[[万国表|万国]]等品牌）的帮助下，成立了朗格公司（Lange Uhren GmbH）并重新注册了朗格品牌，总部依然选址于德国格拉斯许特，并于1994年推出了重建后的第一款腕表。<ref name=":14">{{Cite web|url=https://www.hautehorlogerie.org/en/brands/history/h/a-lange-soehne/|title=History - Fondation de la Haute Horlogerie|website=www.hautehorlogerie.org|access-date=2018-12-14|archive-date=2020-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201205231424/https://www.hautehorlogerie.org/en/brands/history/h/a-lange-soehne/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="thelocal">{{cite web|url=http://www.thelocal.de/20100519/27295|title=Saxon craftsmanship before its time|accessdate=24 May 2016|last=McGrane|first=Sally|publisher=[[The_Local|The Local]]|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304063345/http://www.thelocal.de/20100519/27295|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2000年，朗格被瑞士[[历峰集团|历峰集团]]（Richemont Group）收购，现今朗格公司年产量约5千枚。<ref name=":14" /><ref name="nytimes2">{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2015/11/27/fashion/at-home-with-a-lange-sohne.html|title=At Home With A. Lange & Söhne|accessdate=24 May 2016|date=27 November 2015|work=The New York Times|archive-date=2015-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151206023331/http://www.nytimes.com/2015/11/27/fashion/at-home-with-a-lange-sohne.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/carolbesler/2019/01/25/sihh-2019-a-lange-sohne-richard-lange-jumping-seconds-with-black-dial/#6441a6852fe7|title=SIHH 2019: A. Lange & Söhne Richard Lange Jumping Seconds With Black Dial|last=Besler|first=Carol|language=en|website=Forbes|access-date=2019-02-24|accessdate=|author=|date=|publisher=|archive-date=2019-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190827135742/https://www.forbes.com/sites/carolbesler/2019/01/25/sihh-2019-a-lange-sohne-richard-lange-jumping-seconds-with-black-dial/#6441a6852fe7|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

2017年，沃尔特·朗格去世，享年92岁。<ref name=":22">{{Cite web|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/elizabethdoerr/2018/04/17/making-history-unique-a-lange-sohne-1815-homage-to-walter-lange-gets-set-to-hit-auction-block/|title=Making History: Unique A. Lange & Söhne 1815 Homage To Walter Lange Gets Set To Hit Auction Block|last=Doerr|first=Elizabeth|language=en|website=Forbes|access-date=2018-12-14|archive-date=2019-08-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190831011644/https://www.forbes.com/sites/elizabethdoerr/2018/04/17/making-history-unique-a-lange-sohne-1815-homage-to-walter-lange-gets-set-to-hit-auction-block/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>[https://www.gq-magazine.co.uk/gallery/best-mens-watches-2018 The GQ Watch Guide 2018] {{Wayback|url=https://www.gq-magazine.co.uk/gallery/best-mens-watches-2018 |date=20180710023618 }} [[GQ_magazine|GQ magazine]], 15 August 2018</ref>

== 钟表制造 ==
[[File:Marine-Chronometer.A.Lange&Soehne.1948.jpg|缩略图]]
所有的朗格手表均为机械表，没有[[石英钟|石英表]]。朗格的手表均为自己研发、生产并组装。<ref name="dna2">{{cite web|url=http://www.dnaindia.com/lifestyle/report-when-passion-and-precision-meet-in-watchmaking-2146193|title=When passion and precision meet in watchmaking|accessdate=24 May 2016|date=17 November 2015|work=dna|archive-date=2016-02-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160219062606/http://www.dnaindia.com/lifestyle/report-when-passion-and-precision-meet-in-watchmaking-2146193|dead-url=no}}</ref> 除了少数例外，朗格手表的表壳均为黄金、玫瑰金、白金或铂金制造。

朗格表的设计和外观都具有独特的格拉斯许特风格，与瑞士表的风格迥然不同。譬如，朗格表的机芯均采用镍银（German Silver）为制作材料，而不是瑞士表所使用的镀黄铜。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.forbes.com/forbes-life-magazine/2008/0915/120.html|title=It's About Time|accessdate=24 May 2016|date=6 September 2008|last=Forster|first=Jack|work=Forbes|archive-date=2019-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190822042100/https://www.forbes.com/forbes-life-magazine/2008/0915/120.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

朗格的机械表包括手动上链和自动上链，同时拥有复杂表款，包括[[萬年曆錶|万年历]]、计时功能等。2018年1月，朗格推出了三秒追针计时器（Triple Split chronograph），是对传统的双秒追针计时器（double/split-second chronogrpah）的推进。<ref name=":5">{{Cite web|url=https://www.hodinkee.com/articles/a-lange-and-sohne-triple-split-introducing|title=Introducing: The A. Lange & Söhne Triple Split, The World's First Triple Rattrapante Chronograph|last=January 15|first=Jack Forster|language=en|last2=2018|website=HODINKEE|access-date=2019-01-16|archive-date=2020-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201210214538/https://www.hodinkee.com/articles/a-lange-and-sohne-triple-split-introducing|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.watchtime.com/wristwatch-industry-news/watches/power-of-three-introducing-the-a-lange-sohne-triple-split/|title=Power of Three: Introducing the A. Lange & Söhne Triple Split|date=2018-01-15|last=Bernardo|first=Written byMark|language=en-US|website=WatchTime - USA's No.1 Watch Magazine|access-date=2019-01-16|archive-date=2019-08-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190829210936/https://www.watchtime.com/wristwatch-industry-news/watches/power-of-three-introducing-the-a-lange-sohne-triple-split/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 新的计时器能够比较两个同时发生的事件的持续时间，最长时长可达12小时、精度达六分之一秒。<ref name=":5" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.alange-soehne.com/en/timepieces/triple-split|title=TRIPLE SPLIT {{!}} A. Lange & Söhne|website=www.alange-soehne.com|access-date=2019-01-16|archive-date=2021-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210627221654/https://www.alange-soehne.com/en/timepieces/triple-split|dead-url=no}}</ref>

