=== 朗格1815 ===
一般而言，朗格1815表款是为了纪念品牌创始人费迪南德·阿道夫·朗格。费迪南德·阿道夫·朗格于1815年出生，1845年创立了朗格品牌。<ref name=":7">{{Cite web|url=http://www.alange-soehne.com/en/timepieces/family-1815|title=Family 1815|language=en|website=A. Lange & Söhne|access-date=2018-12-19|archive-date=2021-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210510080950/https://www.alange-soehne.com/en/timepieces/family-1815|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.alange-soehne.com/en/stories/1815-watch-family|title=A tribute to Ferdinand Adolph Lange’s heritage|language=en|website=A. Lange & Söhne|access-date=2018-12-19|archive-date=2021-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123230324/https://www.alange-soehne.com/en/stories/1815-watch-family|dead-url=no}}</ref> 朗格1815 系列也包含一些复杂表款，比如计时功能、年历、陀飞轮、万年历等。<ref name=":7" /><ref name=":6">{{Cite web|url=https://www.christies.com/features/A-Lange-and-Sohne-watches-collecting-guide-9360-1.aspx|title=Collecting guide: A. Lange & SÃ¶hne watches {{!}} Christie's|language=en|website=www.christies.com|access-date=2019-01-17|archive-date=2019-09-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190902045043/https://www.christies.com/features/A-Lange-and-Sohne-watches-collecting-guide-9360-1.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 朗格1号 ===
朗格1号（Lange 1）是1990年朗格品牌重建后推出的第一系列表款之一。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.alange-soehne.com/en/timepieces/family-lange1|title=Family LANGE 1|language=en|website=A. Lange & Söhne|access-date=2018-12-19|archive-date=2021-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210416073035/https://www.alange-soehne.com/en/timepieces/family-lange1|dead-url=no}}</ref> 朗格1号的风格独特，其表盘设计成离散、不对称状，并且具备大比例的日期显示。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.alange-soehne.com/en/stories/lange1-watch-family|title=The living legend among Lange watches|language=en|website=A. Lange & Söhne|access-date=2018-12-19|archive-date=2020-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201022204813/https://www.alange-soehne.com/en/stories/lange1-watch-family|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2012年，在瑞士日内瓦的国际高级钟表沙龙 （Salon International de la Haute Horlogerie）上，朗格推出了全新的朗格1号，包括带有[[陀飞轮|陀飞轮]]、万年历的腕表以及重塑的大朗格1号（Grand Lange 1），还包括朗格1号白金款的时区表。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.thewatchreviewsite.co.uk/?p=1658 |title=Lange 1 Time Zone in white gold |access-date=2018-12-20 |archive-date=2012-07-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120715084519/http://www.thewatchreviewsite.co.uk/?p=1658 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

